# Keep binary assets byte-for-byte — core.autocrlf must never touch these.
# (The setup-guide PDF is ASCII85-encoded so git would otherwise mis-detect it
# as text and apply CRLF conversion, corrupting it.)
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.zip binary
*.xlsx binary
